A FEW RESILIENT countries and sectors have helped cushion the effects of a trade and manufacturing slowdown in the euro zone. But can that continue? Also, Tyler Cowen, an economist and blogger, stands up for big business. And, it’s all in the small print – why it matters that consumers neither read nor understand the contracts they sign. Simon Long hosts. Runtime: 16 min    Listen on: Apple Podcasts | Spotify | Google | Stitcher | TuneIn